title: Approach AAVE and request advantage to having AAVEGOTCHI in a wallet that borrows from AAVE.
body: Holding a Gotchi in your wallet reduces APR on borrowing for some instruments. Example borrowing WBTC is 4%. Rate with AAVEGOTCHI in wallet 3.8%. Lots of options for promotions etc for AAVE and AAVEGOTCHI team.
author: 0x7F73D6242d5731E89D0d3A2c3E7Dbd3795b5dA8D
